36654>>>>>>>        Move (DateSetMinute(dtTime, (Integer(sMinutes)))) to dtTime
36655>>>>>>>        Move (DateSetSecond(dtTime, (Integer(sSeconds)))) to dtTime
36656>>>>>>>        
36656>>>>>>>        Function_Return dtTime
36657>>>>>>>    End_Function
