37382>>>        //  Hide header & apply nice background style
37382>>>        Send HideHeader to ghoWebApp
37383>>>        WebSet psCSSClass of ghoWebApp to "LoginBackground"
37384>>>    End_Procedure
37385>>>    
37385>>>End_Object
